    "title": "Building a statewide Data Science Community of Practice",
    "excerpt": "<p>In January 2025, CalData launched the Data Science Community of Practice. It gathers data scientists to: The community helps us understand the landscape of data science across the state. It also connects people who may work in silos. They have a safe space to ask questions, collaborate, and learn from each other. Building the community &#8230; <a title=\"Building a statewide Data Science Community of Practice\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/2026/04/07/building-statewide-data-science-community-practice/\" aria-label=\"More on Building a statewide Data Science Community of Practice\">Read more</a></p>\n",
